# Assets

- No npm/webpack — plain CSS/JS in `public/assets/`
- Use `asset()` helper for URLs in PHP templates
- Scripts: prefer `defer`; no inline secrets
- Separate contexts: `analytics.js`+`consent.js` (storefront), `admin-analytics.js` (admin GTM), `visitor-track.js` (local tracking)
- Do not merge unrelated JS bundles without explicit need
